### 判断问题类型

```python
MUST_FIX_TYPES = {"Bug", "Security", "Rule violation", "Reliability", "bug_risk", "security"}

def is_must_fix(issue_type: str) -> bool:
    for type_name in MUST_FIX_TYPES:
        if type_name.lower() in issue_type.lower():
            return True
    return False
```

