├── section#moreactivities (继续赚取板块)
│   ├── 积分统计: <span class="font-semibold">40</span><span class="text-neutralFg3">/40</span>
│   └── grid容器 (lg:grid-cols-2 2xl:grid-cols-3)
│       ├── <a href="rewards.bing.com/referandearn/"> 推荐好友 (跳过) </a>
